text: W. D. Irvine was an American football coach. He served as the head football coach a Franklin & Marshall College in Lancaster, Pennsylvania. He held that position for the 1890 season. His coaching record at Franklin & Marshall was 8–2. ==Head coaching record== ==References== Category:Year of birth missing Category:Year of death missing Category:Franklin & Marshall Diplomats football coaches
